Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:34.51,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,New School Term
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew this would happen, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.26,0:01:42.27,CenterSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Year, Class B
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.26,0:01:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because of the class changes in the 2nd year,\NMr. Hayashida was no longer my teacher.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They'll sell out\Nof the double minced meat sandwich!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever! I'm getting the fried chicken\Npotato salad sandwich!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:01:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The ball is your friend!\NI'm prepared to shock the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is it true he's a year older?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then he's repeating the year? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he plays shogi or something.\NI'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Isn't shogi a game for old men?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shogi? Game? At home? An otaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.97,0:02:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why he's repeating?\NBecause he ditched so much school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh. Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I'm getting out of here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the class changed,\Nmy classmates immediately formed groups.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Within those groups that have already formed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}how am I supposed to join them when I'm\Na loser with no courage or skills to do so?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mind if I sit with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, no. More normal, less eager.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, would it be okay if I ate with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like that, smoothly...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:03:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mean, if I could do that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wouldn't be eating lunch\Nby myself for 11 years!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nope. It's impossible.\NI'll definitely stumble on the words.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, this is what I imagined.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just have to bear it alone quietly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}2 Years
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two more years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}730 Days
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}17,520 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just two more years of being alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}1,051,200 Minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}63,072,000 Seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}More importantly, the rank-deciding competition\Nstarts in June, and I need to focus{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}on my upcoming matches\Nin the Newcomers' battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shogi Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The rank-deciding competition.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are 34 players in my Rank C-1.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From among them, ten matches\Nare arranged by lottery.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only the top two players\Nare then promoted to B-2.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nikaidou's name wasn't listed\Non the schedule of matches.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this, Kiriyama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you in Sendagaya now?\NI'm on my way! Wait for me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So now we'll just have to clash\Nin the Newcomers' battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad that you're in A block\Nwhile I'm in B block,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but we'll just have to keep winning\Nso we can meet in the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! Did you just say the finals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are limits in making snap decisions, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just speaking the truth!\NDon't falter, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...is only beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}L-L-Legend?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And why is it "ours"?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Jiggle Jiggle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yep. Looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah. I'll have to do my best.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because that's all I can do for both{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Newcomers' battle\Nand the rank-deciding competition.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll do my best.\NOne move at a time again, from the start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One move at a time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, you bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... Mr. Hayashida?\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't just abandon\Nthe students you were with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What else am I supposed to do\Nwhen I see a student make that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to run after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-A face like "that?" A-A face like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tousle\NTousle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A face like this! Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- So, um...\N- What, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:06:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for you to have lunch with me,\Neven though you're not my teacher this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just saw the gloomy look on the face\Nof my former introverted student
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,who barely passed the attendance requirement\Ndue to "certain circumstances."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I told them that, they said,\N"Mr. Hayashida, hurry up and go to him!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you casually make me sound like\Na loser while you get to play the hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I want to be invited\Nto the students' Christmas party this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm desperate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But still,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,why did you come back here, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the new school term of a new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't make an effort now,\Nwhen would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you are making an effort, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can't tell you to\N"do your best" any more than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I had an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:06:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a shogi club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shogi club?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll be the faculty adviser.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then it wouldn't be strange\Nfor me to look after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'd be your adviser.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can easily say that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With five members and a faculty adviser,\Nyou can make a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to find four more members.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find... Find how?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think we can find them so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:34.58,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just\Nremembered\Nsomething
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Stare
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you were about to say "but"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you want to take another shot\Nat being a high school student?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was it to eat lunch alone on the stairs like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not, right, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:07:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Will this make it seem like\NI'm not running away?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"What if I'm only pretending not to run away?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The truth is, it's always...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's always weighed heavily on my mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'd realized it, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this rate, things would only become\Nmore painful for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It hit me at that time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If only I could blend in so well like that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}just how... how very...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...how very happy could I be?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mr. Hayashida. Can I ask you to be\Nthe club's faculty adviser?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sure will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}And Kiriyama, of course, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You'll coach me too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yes. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! There it is!\NI get a professional's coaching for free!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get beyond the wall\Nin "Ama, 4th dan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's this jerk I want to beat\Non Net Shogi 24!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hayashida, a minute ago, I was moved\Nby your kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Faculty Room
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:24.52,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nobody. Nobody wants to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What? Is shogi really so minor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Everyone's like, "Shogi? Sorry, I'm not\Nreally interested." What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}When I love it so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}There's nothing for you to apologize about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I kind of feel responsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}After School Bunsen Burner's Club\NCurrently Active
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Noguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Waft
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:55.18,3rd,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*3rd-\NYear
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It stinks in here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hayashida, long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you guys doing this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Packed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Sticky{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,\Nwe're harvesting natto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:04.56,3rd,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*3rd-\NYear
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, but why "harvest" natto at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What we do is wrap steamed soybeans\Nin a straw of rice and let it sit for a day
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,at about 40 degrees, which allows the bacillus\Nsubtilis in the straw to spread to the soybeans,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and through this proliferation,\Nfermentation occurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah. I didn't actually ask\N"how" you're doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this really is natto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:21.49,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sticky
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:21.49,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got offered some
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're eating it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once in a while, you don't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, where'd you get\Nthe straw of rice from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:32.96,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*3rd-Year
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Is Self-sufficiency Possible\Nat a High School?"\Nby Eisaku Noguchi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did it for my thesis here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I harvested it while growing rice\Non the school roof last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that thesis? Who are you\Npresenting it to? I mean, what's it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you can't practice\Nself-sufficiency at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know where to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I almost forgot my original purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Noguchi, do you know how to play shogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shogi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My grandfather taught me to play it\Nwhen I was young, but that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But indeed, that is a deep game, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So listen, we're trying to put together\Na shogi club,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but we're having a hard time\Ngetting the five members.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now we've finally got someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The continued existence of my\NAfter School Burners Club is in peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the club may be disbanded\Nat the club budget meeting in May.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? But you had a lot of members.\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The upperclassmen all graduated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. Those members\Nwere all older than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:41.66,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two Years Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this the Science Club?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}*1st-Year
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- Senpai?\N- No, Club President!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}*Upperclassmen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:49.16,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*1st-Year
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:49.16,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*Upperclassmen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:49.16,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeay\NWow
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they were marvelous mentors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From the day I joined the club, even though\NI was a first-year, they called me "Senpai."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:12:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to keep the club going and pass on\Nthe wonder of science to younger students,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but with only four members left, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I could only complete this thesis...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you did finish, I don't know\Nif it would pass on the joy of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you guys combine to form one club?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:26.24,LeftSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One\Nmember
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:26.24,RightSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Four\Nmembers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Total = 5 People
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That makes sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Then without further ado,\Nhow about we play a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've kind of been holding back, but from now on,\NI can play a lot of matches with Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm the faculty adviser.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Noguchi. I feel like I should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For imposing on you every time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually kind of excited about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After my grandfather passed away,\NI wasn't able to find anyone to play with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still just a novice,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but will you teach me too, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}After School Bunsen Burner's Club\NCurrently Active
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, the After School Burners Club{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}became the After School Shogi Science Club.\NOr for short, the Sho-sci Club.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}After School Shogi Science Club\NCurrently Active
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A club. A club, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And a shogi club at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See? Like I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the way home,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In my experience, I've found that "it's easier\Nto do something than worry about it."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or that's about 80% right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...he said it with a grin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:55.04,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,New School Term
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:59.04,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The seat next to me is always empty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to sit next to Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Teacher? Teacher, Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I change seats?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off, Kaneda. Don't be stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaneda, just hurry up and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are other open seats.\NTeacher, it's fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, do what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fourth grade, group five is leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hurry up and sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At a time like this, I always think...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you don't want to sit by me, that's fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm lucky the seat next to you was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But could you be a little quieter about it\Nand not make a scene?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}He's always so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But once the bus pulled out,\NI felt a little relieved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, it was much, much easier this way\Nthan to sit next to someone who hates me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. We're going to have lunch now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the bathroom, finish everything up,\Nand be back at the bus by 1:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then you're on your own. Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Shoot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}What am I supposed to do here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}The field is huge!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}There's no escape zone at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Eating my lunch all alone\Nin a wide open field like this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I'll stand out so much that I'll die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And worse, if Teacher finds me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Kiriyama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are you eating alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's no good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Today's Topic: Why do you exclude Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll inevitably become the focus of next week's\Nhomeroom assignment!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Think about this seriously, everyone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}What the heck is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That would be the worst.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Squeak\NSqueak
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}It's tough enough\Njust having everyone hate me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}To be put on display on top of that\Nwouldn't solve anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}It would only bring attention\Nto the fact that I'm despised.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I want to avoid that no matter what!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a little far, but I'll go over there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be okay. This'll work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Quietly, and don't jog over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I just walk over slowly, like normal,\NI won't stand out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Normally, normally...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I did it!\NI made it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold! And damp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know! It'll be fine\Nif I put down my clear file folder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of ants!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't crawl on my lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nhow do ants carry away candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they lick it, melting tiny pieces\Nat a time to carry off?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With their little mouths...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}#234 Checkmate within 117 Moves
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I made a copy of this from Dad's book.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Checkmate in 117 moves...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You solved it? The 85 moves one?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's incredible, Rei!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't solve that one\Nuntil I was in middle school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My adoptive father is a shogi player.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He turned professional at 19.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if Dad will be happy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}if I solve this problem, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gather around! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's 1:30 already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! I haven't cleaned up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, uh, have I forgotten anything? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The candy! It's that small already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I had no idea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Despite being so little,\Nants melted candy at an incredible speed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're late! Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, the bathroom was crowded...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be leaving. Is there anyone\Nwhose seat neighbor hasn't come back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Kiriyama, where's your seat neighbor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. There was no one here from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then we're all here, huh?\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"There was no one here from the start."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The moment I answered him,\NI felt a lump in my throat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Teacher, will the seat next to me\Nbe empty for the rest of my life?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Next, seat 5.\NThe match with Sugawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}To me, that was a magic ticket.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}As long as I had that ticket,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}somebody would always,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:19:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}automatically,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}sit across from me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I encountered many different kinds of people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Who is this little brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're too good! Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, I'll walk with you to the station,\Nsince it's already dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, drink this. Do you like coco?\NDammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Some were kind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And of course...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're pretty weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I heard Kouda\Ntook you in as his disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...some didn't like me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But as long as I kept fighting,\Nsomebody would always sit before me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}"This is a ticket."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}As long as I have this ticket,\NI belong somewhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:21:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This ticket was my lifeline.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't have to arrive anywhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I could just keep on riding.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was fine with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I got off this train,\NI would have nowhere to go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This ticket alone would take me to tomorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had to hold on to this ticket\Nlike my life depended on it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to protect it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...at all costs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kiriyama. Kiriyama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Kiriyama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you spacing out for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sit your butt down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He moved, and it was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The 5-c-Pawn+ being sacrificed\Nwas a great move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With same, Gold and 7-g-Rook, what's next?\NKiriyama, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}How much time is left?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shogi Dragon Fujimoto has eight minutes.\NBrother has less than three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding the 7-g-Rook, crush it.\NTake the initiative by moving 6-d-Gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.58,0:22:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6-d-Gold? Not the 7-c-Pawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you did that,\Nit'd be tough with the 6-b-Bishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.17,0:22:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not like I've changed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.22,0:22:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the people around me haven't changed either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.02,0:22:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just that while\Ndesperately playing and playing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}every single day until it seemed like\Nmy head would spin,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day, I realized{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.62,0:22:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that other people were traveling with me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.62,0:22:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}towards the same place,\Nwhere the light was shining.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.18,0:23:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And today too,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.01,0:23:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}someone is sitting across from me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.56,0:23:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Another new story will begin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our journey towards the shining light\Nwill continue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:43.00,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.30,0:24:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for watching\N“March Comes in Like a Lion”.
